Open Cart - Fix Empty Images
- This script will find any empty image 
  field from each product and set it to 
  the no_image.jpg default no image file
- Must be installed in the root of the 
  OpenCart install
- To use a custom default image, simply save 
  your file as /image/no_image.jpg
- Execute script by navigating to it in 
  your browser http://your_install.com/update_images.php